                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Tassilo"
                                >Tassilo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">vir devotus</rs> filius bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Autchis">Autchisi</name></persName>,
                            <foreign>pur riservandosi la piena disponibilità di tutti i suoi beni
                            finché sarà in vita e di prendere ulteriori disposizioni testamentarie,
                            vuole che quanto resterà intestato vada a</foreign>
                        <persName key="#Priests #testamentaryLinkWith"
                            ><name>Rachipertu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests ">presbitero</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Priests #testamentaryLinkWith"><name>Rottelmi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Priests #testamentaryLinkWith"><name>Aurulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Priests #testamentaryLinkWith"><name>Gundipertu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <persName key="#testamentaryLinkWith"
                                ><name>Fermuso</name></persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name>Petronaci</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#testamentaryLinkWith"><name>Cunimundo</name></persName>
                        <foreign>che dovranno vendere</foreign>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">omnis res mea</rs> quanta ad me pertene et
                        iniudicata vel non data remansere, tam res movile quam et inmoviles seo qui
                        se moventibus uviqui in colivet locum ad ius meum pertene; (…) excepto parte
                        mea de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name>Raduli</name></persName> in
                            <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#places/438"
                            >Corsania</placeName>, et parte mea de <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> ubi quondam <persName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name>Guntulo</name></persName>
                        massario nostro resede, in loco <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >Vetusiano</placeName>; et parte mea de <rs key="#Cafagia">cafagio</rs>
                        nostro in loco <placeName key="#Cafagia">Monacciaticho</placeName>, quem iam
                        antea iudicavi. <foreign>Se non potessero vendere quei beni</foreign>, volo
                        ut de ipsis rebus meis aveas <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/79">Sancti
                            Petri</orgName> in loco qui dicitor <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/85">Monte Virde</placeName>, a quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Walfredus">Walfridi</name></persName> fundatum est, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">omnia portionem meam de res </rs>quanta avire
                        videor in loco ubi vocatur [<placeName key="#Landed_possessions">ad
                            Chint</placeName>; et aveas] <rs key="#Mother_churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> de episcopio parte mea de <rs key="#Cafagia"
                            >gavagio</rs> nostro in loco <placeName key="#Cafagia" ref="#places/91"
                            >Cornino</placeName>, uvi vocatur ad <placeName key="#Cafagia"
                            >Chinzia</placeName>, qui est prope <rs key="#Cafagia">gavagius</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Cafagia" ref="#juridical_persons/68">Sancti
                        Martini</orgName>; et aveas <rs key="#Monasteries">monastherio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/603">Sancti
                            Petri</orgName> in <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/336">Campo
                            Magiore</placeName> parte mea de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casas</rs> vel <rs key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> in loco
                            <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#places/1022">Terrinca</placeName>; et aveas <rs key="#Churches"
                            >eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/246">Sancti
                            Ieorgi</orgName>, ubi <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iordanus"
                                >Iordanni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> fuit, parte mea de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> in loco <placeName
                            key="#Testamentum/iudicatum #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#places/438">Corsania</placeName>, excepto <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name>Ruduli</name></persName>,
                        quem iam <rs key="#Testamentum/iudicatum">iudicata</rs> aveo; et aveas <rs
                            key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/70">Fridiani</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> mea sub <placeName
                            key="#Venditio #Landed_possessions" ref="#places/205"
                            >Monticello</placeName>, qui fuit quondam <persName
                            key=" #Landed_possessions"><name>Arochisi</name></persName> quantum mihi
                        da filii ipsius <rs key="#Venditio">abvine</rs> in integrum, in finito; (…)
                        et aveas similiter parte mea de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casa</rs> in loco <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >Cornino</placeName>, uvi [<persName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >Ar…]sulo</persName> reside; et <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/272">Sancte Marie, qui est
                                <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/4">ad porta Sancti
                                Cervasi</placeName></orgName>, volo ut aveas parte mea de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> in loco <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Persiniano</placeName>; et volo ut aveas <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/130">Sancti
                            Salvatori</orgName> in loco <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/315">Sexto</placeName> parte mea de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> in loco <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Pinistello</placeName> et ad
                            <placeName>Arno</placeName> uvi vocamus <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/1023">ad Noce</placeName>; et
                        volo ut aveas <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                                <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Iusti</orgName> ad <placeName key="#Churches">Ranule</placeName>
                                <rs key="#Hay/fodder">prato</rs> meo ad <placeName key="#Hay/fodder #Canals"><rs key="#Canals"
                                >fossa</rs> Petrosula</placeName> in integrum; et volo ut aveas <rs
                            key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancte Reparate</orgName>, qui est prope <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monastherio</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Martini</orgName>, qui fuit quondam
                            <persName>Sicheradi</persName>, parte mea de <rs>res</rs> in loco
                            <placeName>Nobule</placeName>; et volo ut <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs> illa qui mihi <rs key="#Venditio">obvinet</rs> da quondam
                            <persName>Tachipertu</persName>
                        <placeName>ad Archo</placeName>, qui latum tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> de filii quondam
                            <persName>Garisindi</persName>, ut eas aveas <rs key="#Churches"
                            >eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Petri qui vocatur <rs key="#Monasteries">monastherio</rs>
                            <persName>Somualdi</persName></orgName>; et volo ut aveas parte mea de
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <placeName>trans Auserclo</placeName>, qui caput tene in ipso
                            <placeName>Auserclo</placeName> et alio caput tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> de filii quondam
                            <persName>Burriche</persName>, <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Donati</orgName>. <foreign>Alle</foreign> nepotis meas
                            <persName>Sindiperga</persName>, <persName>Radalperga</persName> et
                            <persName>Adalperga</persName>, portionem meam de <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs>
                        <persName>Arualdi</persName> de <placeName>Lunata</placeName> in loco
                            <placeName>Tappuniano</placeName> et parte mea de <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> quondam
                            <persName>Aufridi</persName> in loco <placeName>Longize</placeName> (…)
                        cum parte mea de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> in
                            <placeName>Tempaniano</placeName>, ubi reside quondam
                            <persName>Antuninulo</persName> (…); et similiter portionem meam de <rs
                            key="#Salae">sala</rs> vel de <rs key="#Demesnes">sundrio</rs> meo in
                        loco <placeName>Longize</placeName>, quantum mihi exinde competent, et <rs
                            key="#Salae">sala</rs> mea in loco […] <placeName><rs>vico</rs>
                            <persName>Willeradi</persName></placeName>, cum omnia ad se pertinentem,
                        unam cum <rs key="#Cereals">terra</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineas</rs> (…);
                            <foreign>devono vendere inoltre</foreign> omnis <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terre</rs> mei quantae ad me hic circa
                                <placeName><rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> ista</placeName> non
                        iudicate remansere. (…) si eam venundare non potueritis volo ut vos ipsa aut
                        in <rs key="#Hospitals">sinodochio</rs> aut in <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monastherio</rs> vel in tale <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs> faciatis
                        unde mihi et vobis mercidem eveniat (…). Et volo ut omnis <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Slave">hominis</rs> meis mihi pertinentis vos <rs
                            key="#Freedman">liveris circa altare</rs> demettere deveatis et eorum
                        cartulam absolutionis emettere diveatis; sic tamen nominative volo de <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Slave">servis vel mancipias minesterialis</rs> ut
                        vos <rs key="#Freedman">livertare</rs> diveatis
                            <persName>Teudipertulo</persName>, et aveas pro servitio suo <rs
                            key="#Petiae">petia de terra</rs> sub <placeName>Monticello</placeName>
                        prope areas <persName>Perteradi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerici</rs>, qui mihi <rs key="#Commutatio">per
                            cambio obvinet</rs> da <persName>Gausperto</persName>, qui est rector
                            <rs key="#Churches">eclesie</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Fridiani</orgName>; et volo ut <rs key="#Freedman">liveru
                            demettere diveatis</rs>
                        <persName>Cianci</persName>, et aveas <rs key="#Petiae">petias de terra</rs>
                        prope areas de filii <persName>Pertualdi</persName>, qui <rs key="#Venditio"
                            >mihi obvine</rs> da filii quondam <persName>Ermerisci</persName>; et
                        volo ut <rs key="#Freedman">liveri demettere diveatis</rs>
                        <persName>Alipertulo</persName>, <persName>Audipertulo</persName>, et
                            <persName>Maxcellio</persName>, et aveas portionem mea de res in
                            <placeName>Ponpiano</placeName>, ubi reside quondam
                            <persName>F[…;</persName> et vo]lo ut <rs key="#Freedman">liverum
                            demettere diveatis</rs>
                        <persName>Fusculo</persName>, et aveas portionem de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> in loco
                            <placeName>Longize</placeName>, cum parte de i[psa <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs>], quantum exinde ei da
                        germani eius pertene; et de <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave">manciapias</rs>
                        volo ut livere demettere diveatis T<persName>e[…</persName> de]
                            <placeName>Corsania</placeName> et <persName>Silbula</persName>,
                            <persName>Liutpergula</persName> et eorum <rs key="#Freedman">cartulam
                            abpsolutionis </rs>emettere diveatis. <foreign>Lascia poi alle
                            nipoti</foreign>: in primis Sindiperga de ipsa <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Slave">mancipias</rs> mea una <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Slave">ancella</rs> nomine
                            <persName>Dominica</persName>; Radalperga volo ut aveas filia
                            <persName>Luccili</persName> nomina <persName>Luciula</persName>; et
                        Adalperga volo ut aveas filia <persName>Autule</persName> de
                            <placeName>Nobule</placeName>. Et volo ut <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        illa qui mihi <rs key="#Venditio">obvine</rs> da <persName>Bonulo</persName>
                        de <placeName>Ispardaco</placeName>, qui est sub <rs>casa</rs>
                        <persName>Liutpertuli</persName>, ut aveas <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Martini</orgName>, qui est ad <placeName>Terra
                            Russula</placeName>. Et volo ut <rs key="#Freedman">livera demettere
                            diveatis</rs>
                        <persName>Allula</persName>. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: auri soledos nomero
                        mille quinienti <foreign>e in duplum</foreign>. Et quod minime memoravimus,
                        similiter volo ut <rs key="#Animals">nutriminas</rs> mea, sive menuris vel
                        maioris, quante aveo, volo ut ipse vos similiter vendere diveatis (…). Actum
                            <placeName>Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: +
                        Tassuni viri devoti; + <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"
                            >Teupertu</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filio quondam
                            <persName>Sanituli</persName> testis; + […] testis; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary">Ratfusu</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Notary"
                            >Wistripert</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics">Willeradus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">Teutpertu</persName> (<rs
                            key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">vir devotus</rs>).
                            <foreign>Copia</foreign>: <persName key="#Copyist #Other_clerics"
                            >Rachiprandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>Muratori 1738-1742: I, 876; MDL IV/1, 63 (<foreign>ad an</foreign>. 766);
                    reg. MDL V/2, n. 106; CDL II, 214, pp. 237-243; ChLA, XXXIV, 1000.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
